high_descs: Head left to reach the pencilcase.
Pick up the pencilcase from under the table.
Head to exit the room on the left and turn left to walk down the passage to reach the round coffeetable.
Put the pencilcase on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the PencilCase on the CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the desk on your right.
Pick up pencil case from under the desk.
Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the coffee table.
Place pencil case on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Shifting pencil case from one place to another.

high_descs: Walk straight into the room, then turn left and walk to the pencilcase and turn to face it.
Pick up the pencilcase off the floor.
Turn around 3/4 then walk through the doorway, hang a left and walk down the hallway into the living room and walk to between the shelves and coffeetable and turn to face the coffeetable.
Set the flashlight on the back of the coffeetable just to the left of centre.
anns.task_desc: Bring the PencilCase to the CoffeeTable.
